# ShellShade meta directory - automatically generated files
# These directories contain temporary/build artifacts that should not be committed

# home/ - Persistent container home directory
# Contains: shell history, tool caches (npm, gradle, pnpm, etc.), application configs
# This is your personal container state, not project source code
home/

# augments/ - Generated Dockerfiles for image augmentation
# Contains: Automatically generated Dockerfiles when base images need modification
# to work with shellshade's entrypoint injection. These are build artifacts.
augments/
